page.name: Elite Wand of the Sunken Rose III
page.description: Yllmar, the Maw of the Deep swallowed many ships and treasures. This wand belonged to an elite squad of Rose huntresses who must have met their demise in the whirlpool. This item requires a Dragon Amulet to use.

page.name: The Depth's Maw
page.description: Dropping anchor near the massive whirlpool only drew out its occupant: Yllmar, the Depth's Maw, peril to anything that wanders too near to its territory.

properties.complete: Yllmar is defeated, but the whirlpool remains. What could be behind it? Are there other sea serpents out there?
